ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: it's devlunch. be there or be square.

It's a great way to get exposure to the current research going on, though the nomer "developmental psychology" is somewhat of a misnomer. It's not really a focus on dev psych in general, but seems to be pretty specifically focused on Social Cognitive Development - if that's your thing, then great. Some weeks are beter than others.
Very interesting lunch meeting where many leading experts of the field are invited as guest speakers.I would recommend it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I liked the speaker a lot. Their work was mostly very interesting and inspiring.
